OL,3,CFraudulent gardener scammed elderly
OL,4,Cwidow out of #14,500
OL,6,FA landscape gardener has been
OL,7,Fsentenced for his role in a "cruel and
OL,8,Fheartless" scam which saw a widow who
OL,9,Fhad just come out of hospital charged
OL,10,F#14,500 for work that now will cost
OL,11,Fthousands more to fix.
OL,13,FThe 81-year-old victim was contacted
OL,14,Fby Patrick Dunleavy after posting
OL,15,Fonline requesting help for her garden
OL,16,Fwhich was "looking like a jungle"
OL,17,Fafter her extended hospital stay in
OL,18,Fearly June 2023.
