OL,3,CFraudulent gardener scammed elderly
OL,4,Cwidow out of #14,500
OL,6,FDunleavy, also known as Peter John
OL,7,FJames Gerard Dunleavy, replied almost
OL,8,Fimmediate offering to come round the
OL,9,Fsame day, Preston Crown Court was told.
OL,11,FHe agreed a price of #8,000 to carry
OL,12,Fout drainage, groundwork, and
OL,13,Fgardening jobs, with the man, whose
OL,14,Ftrue identity remains unknown, telling
OL,15,Fhis victim he needed to be paid in
OL,16,Fadvance.
OL,18,FHe was given #900 in cash and a cheque
OL,19,Ffor #7,100.
