OL,6,FThe victim was then asked for another
OL,7,F#6,400 after "problems" were
OL,8,Fidentified, including #2,000 to fix a
OL,9,Fbroken pipe.
OL,11,FOn each occasion, the victim was asked
OL,12,Fto pay by debit card into a Lloyds
OL,13,Fbank account, with the address
OL,14,Fmatching the defendant's home address
OL,15,Fon Rolleston Avenue, Manchester.
