OL,3,CFraudulent gardener scammed elderly
OL,4,Cwidow out of #14,500
OL,6,FAfter a complaint to Lancashire's
OL,7,FTrading Standards officers, a
OL,8,Fchartered building engineer carried
OL,9,Fout an inspection which found the work
OL,10,Fto be of such poor quality that, apart
OL,11,Ffrom #650 of materials, it held no
OL,12,Fvalue.
OL,14,FThe court heard that despite paying
OL,15,Fthe men #14,500, the elderly victim
OL,16,Fwas now facing a bill of #4,350 to fix
OL,17,Fthe work.
