OL,6,FCouncillor Joshua Roberts said: "While
OL,7,Flittle is known about the so-called
OL,8,Fworkmen, these offences would not have
OL,9,Fbeen possible without someone to set
OL,10,Fup the Checkatrade and bank accounts
OL,11,Fon their behalf.
OL,13,F"We hope the defendant will find time
OL,14,Fto reflect on how his involvement
OL,15,Fenabled an elderly resident to be
OL,16,Fconned in such a cruel and heartless
OL,17,Fway.
